Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Benigno Aquino assassinated
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043x8v7
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Aug 1983
Shocking assassination of Benigno Aquino presents President Reagan with dilemma over Philippines bases. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less